attributes.review: I downloaded the app because I love rapists. The download took a lot longer than I expected and made my phone crash! I figured the app was secretly laced with a virus so I decided to delete it and find other ways to worship pedophiles. but when i tried to delete it the app took over my phone! The screen turned red and Russian words started rapidly scrolling on the screen! then, a loud siren started blaring from my phone. I couldn’t tell if it was a countdown, a warning siren, or something far worse! To make matters worse, it caused my phone to emit a rancid smell! it was so bad my eyes started to water and my wall paper started to peel! I was so desperate I began frantically finding any way to make the noise and the smells stop! I put my phone in a small cardboard box and then put that box inside another box, and then I mailed that box to myself, and when it arrived... I smashed with a hammer! It was brilliant, brilliant, brilliant, I tell you! Genius I say! Once I had done that I buried it in my backyard next to my beautiful rose bush, but to no suprise the roses died the next day! In fact, my entire back yard died! The grass, the trees, it was like the virus had infected the natural life around it and there was no way of stopping it! Once it reached my house the walls began to deteriorate and my roof completely caved in! I only had time to grab a few shirts and I drove all the way across the country! I went to an Apple store but they refused to serve me because I didn’t want to wear a mask because I care nothing about the health and well being of other people! I was so angry I began licking every surface! Now I live in a small apartment on the west side of Omaha, Nebraska. I have only a pile of clothes to sleep on and I used my buildings computer to write this review because I had to warn the people of America! Do not download this app!
